                Open your developer tab when going through this process, and you can see the cookie
                and the data it contains. Hit the 'Go Home' button to give it another try! Notice the
                state changes each time.</p>
            <div class='button'>
                <a href="/"><button>Go home!</button></a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </body>
